name: The Wooden Stick (Prototype Test)
description:
This is a game called The Wooden Stick, it's just a prototype and I'm testing some stuff with it. You kinda just start off with a wooden stick, slay some cylinders that are completely harmless and yeah.

ESC - Quit the game

R - Restart from the beginning

WASD - To move around

Spacebar - To jump

Left click - To attack

The epic music by Kevin Macleod is called "Dark Pad".

Game made by Sean173.
